2009-02-21 14:03 UTC+0100 Viktor Szakats (harbour.01 syenar hu)
  * bin/hb-func.sh
  * utils/hbmk2/hbmk2.prg
    ! Some three bad typos in recent commit.
    ! Fixed the way build-default GT is supplied via hbmkcfg file.
      (via gtdef= line)
