2008-11-14 20:57 UTC-0800 Pritpal Bedi (pritpal@vouchcac.com)
  * harbour/contrib/gtwvg/gtwvg.c
  * harbour/contrib/gtwvg/wvgsink.c
    ! Pacified some warnings.
    ! Formatting per Harbour standards.

