  * include/hbextern.ch
  * source/rtl/memofile.c
    + Added HB_MEMOREAD() which is identical to MEMOREAD()
      except it won't truncate the last byte (on non-UNIX
      compatible systems) if it's a EOF char.
      See also existing HB_MEMOWRIT().
      [TOMERGE 1.0]

