      cursor position. Xbase++ users can use
         #xtranslate DispOutAt( <x,...> ) => hb_dispOutAt( <x> )
      for Xbase++ compatible code

2008-10-09 20:51 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
