       'fatal error: Internal error: reduce_tree()'
       I didn't test if it actually works, but at least now
       is compiles.
       Bug reported on Pelles C forum.

2008-08-26 22:13 UTC+0200 Viktor Szakats (harbour.01 syenar hu)
