2008-08-06 22:30 UTC-0800 Pritpal Bedi (pritpal@vouchcac.com)
  * harbour/source/rtl/achoice.prg
    + Implemented mouse operations as follows.
      CASE ( nKey == K_MWFORWARD )
         Keyboard( Chr( K_UP ) )
      CASE ( nKey == K_MWBACKWARD )
         Keyboard( Chr( K_DOWN ) )
      CASE nKey == K_LDBLCLK
         Keyboard( Chr( K_ENTER ) )

