              would be necessary.
     ; Please test.

2008-06-27 14:58 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/source/pp/ppcore.c
    ! fixed GPF in expressions like:
         #command CMD => #translate abc => \
