  + harbour/contrib/hbhpdf
    + harbour/contrib/hbhpdf/harupdf.c
    + harbour/contrib/hbhpdf/hpdf.h
      Initial upload of wrappers for HaruPDF Library (http://sourceforge.net/projects/libharu/).
