2008-02-04 09:31 UTC+0100 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/harbour.spec
  * harbour/harbour-ce-spec
  * harbour/harbour-w32-spec
    * updated for new library names

  * harbour/ChangeLog
