2007-11-04 03:40 UTC+0200 Mindaugas Kavaliauskas (dbtopas/at/dbtopas.lt)
  * include/hbapifs.h
  * harbour/source/common/hbfsapi.c
    ! fixed hb_fsFileExists() for DOS
