2007-05-17 00:20 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/TODO
    * removed some not longer necessary TODO/TOFIX

  * harbour/common.mak
  * harbour/source/rtl/Makefile
  - harbour/source/rtl/memoline.c
