      or { "KEY" => MEMOFILED, ... } and optimized results of PLUS operation

  * harbour/utils/hbtest/rt_misc.prg
    * SET EOL to CHR(13) + CHR( 10 ) before MLCTOPOS() tests to avoid false
      alarm on platforms with differ default EOL

