2007-05-12 11:10 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/source/rtl/hbffind.c
    ! fixed typo in my previous commit

2007-05-12 10:48 UTC+0100 Antonio Linares (alinares@fivetechsoft.com)
