       (~20% size reduction).

2007-04-10 14:35 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/include/Makefile
    + added hbregex.h

  * harbour/include/hbclass.ch
    + added support for ENDCLASS LOCK[ED]
    + := <clasname> { <constructorParams,...> }

