2006-09-20 18:40 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * harbour/contrib/rdd_ads/ads1.c
    * synced with recent xHarbour fixes

  * harbour/include/hbdefs.h
