2006-07-10 20:43 UTC+0100 Viktor Szakats (viktor.szakats syenar.hu)

   By Marek Paliwoda:

   * harbour/makefile.vc
     + Generalized linker flags (LDFLAGS) and small exe generation
       improvements.

