2004-02-27 12:37 UTC+0100 Viktor Szakats <viktor.szakats@syenar.hu>

   * source/rtl/teditor.prg
     ! Fixed a Bound error in GetParagraph which came up when
       using <Del> in wrap mode, in the last line I guess.
