    * source/vm/itemapi.c
    * check for a loop in variable de-referencing was added
    The following code:
    var := IIF( .T., @var, var )
    is causing that the variable is referencing itself
    (valid syntax in Clipper)

    * source/vm/macro.c
    * fixed to link correctly with WATCOM linker


