   From Jose Lalin:

   * contrib/libmisc/dates2.c
     - removed all occurences of:
       char * szDateFormat[]
       sprintf( szDateFormat, "%04i%02i%02i", (int) lYear, (int) lMonth, (int) lDay );
       hb_retds( szDateFormat );
     + replaced with:
       hb_retd( lYear, lMonth, lDay );
     * This will speed up things a bit.

