19990903-19:35 EDT David G. Holm <dholm@jsd-llc.com>
  * source/rtl/console.c
    ! Added #ifdef HARBOUR_USE_GTAPI/#endif around use of GT API
      functions in the new HB_SETPOSBS() function.
  * source/rtl/filesys.c
