     source/vm/hvm.c
     source/tools/hb_f.c
     Non Harbour standard, sparsly used and redundant types removed.
     - PBYTE -> BYTE * (few occurences)
       BYTEP -> BYTE * (few occurences, non standard)
       PVOID -> void * (1 occurence)
       FARPP -> void ** (few occurences)
       FARP  -> void * (few occurences)

