Mon Jun 07 20:20:32 1999  Gonzalo A. Diethelm  <Gonzalo.Diethelm@jda.cl>
        * config/bin.cf:
        * config/c.cf:
        * config/dir.cf:
        * config/global.cf:
        * config/install.cf:
        * config/lib.cf:
